    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I think any internal types that don't touch ssz-defined datastructures can remain numbers, if they are naturally so.\r\n\r\nI think the spirit of this issue is to have a more literal conformance to https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/dev/specs/phase0/beacon-chain.md#custom-types which defines all numbers in eth2 datastructures as uint64.\r\n",
